OL,7,FA dangerous driver who killed a
OL,8,Fteenage passenger and hospitalised
OL,9,Fanother after driving at double the
OL,10,Fspeed limit while waiting to take part
OL,11,Fin a speed awareness course has had
OL,12,Fhis sentence increased.
OL,14,FAdam Ali, 20, was originally jailed
OL,15,Ffor four years after pleading guilty
OL,16,Fin January to one count of death by
OL,17,Fdangerous driving and another for
OL,18,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,19,Fdriving.
