OL,7,FMinshull Street Crown Court heard that
OL,8,Fon the evening of 15 October 2022, the
OL,9,Funiversity student drove dangerously
OL,10,Fwith three passengers in the car
OL,11,Fhaving passed his test a few months
OL,12,Fearlier.
OL,14,FAli drove through a residential area
OL,15,Fin Audenshaw, Manchester, in wet
OL,16,Fconditions, in excess of 60mph in an
OL,17,Farea with a 30mph speed limit.
OL,18,FHowever, he lost control of the car
OL,19,Fand smashed it into a lamp post.
