OL,7,FBen Burbridge, a 16-year-old passenger
OL,8,Fin the back of Ali's Vauxhall Corsa,
OL,9,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene after
OL,10,Fsuffering catastrophic brain injuries.
OL,12,FThe Solicitor General Lucy Rigby KC MP
OL,13,Fsaid: "Ben Burbridge was only 16 years
OL,14,Fold when he died and he had his whole
OL,15,Ffuture ahead of him. His life was
OL,16,Ftragically cut short by Adam Ali's
OL,17,Fdangerous driving.
