OL,7,FThe court heard that Ali, from Kershaw
OL,8,FLane, Audenshaw, Tameside, had
OL,9,Fpreviously been caught speeding and
OL,10,Fmisusing his car horn, and the fatal
OL,11,Faccident occurred while he was waiting
OL,12,Ffor his speed awareness course to
OL,13,Fstart.
OL,15,FWhile awaiting trial, Ali was caught
OL,16,Fspeeding on two further occasions and
OL,17,Flater caused another road accident
OL,18,Fwhile banned from driving ` all while
OL,19,Finhaling a nitrous oxide canister at
OL,20,Fthe wheel.
